data.description: Welcome to Carriage Park II - the ideal commuter location to Virginia and Maryland, and within a five-minute drive of Historic Harpers Ferry, where the Potomac and Shenandoah Rivers come together to create one of the most picturesque views in West Virginia. And let's not forget about the many outdoor activities this location offers you. This beautiful home, in the exclusive Carriage Park II neighborhood, has 3,892 total finished square feet of living space. Four bedrooms, four and a half bathrooms, a large two-story family room, quartz countertops, a stainless-steel farmhouse sink, and stainless-steel appliances. The upstairs features four bedrooms, each with its own bathroom, including a jack-and-jill bathroom shared by two of the bedrooms.  Hardwood floors throughout, a finished basement with a full bathroom, plenty of storage, with outside access. New roof in 2022 with a 25-year transferrable warranty. Enjoy the backyard with the patio and covered porch, all of this on a flat one-acre lot. An exceptional home, make your appointment today.
